{"tid":1788050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台成F16V戰機亞太維修中心","createTime":"2019-12-18T10:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T11:07:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0c24c3ae45b3fd54fceeaf0b9ba7be30655b0950","tid":1788050,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:59:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191218/EGU73YYCOFGKUKAY3TU726WJ7I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191218%2FEGU73YYCOFGKUKAY3TU726WJ7I%2F&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6gmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=dc273614\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191218%2FEGU73YYCOFGKUKAY3TU726WJ7I%2F&h=2f2d09cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191218/EGU73YYCOFGKUKAY3TU726WJ7I/</a><br />\n<br />\n台成F16V戰機亞太維修中心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191218/large/1576599625_a1fb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576599625_a1fb.gif&h=8e456e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣大選臨近，台美加強軍事合作，展示總統蔡英文國防政策的成就。台灣空軍未來將擁有210架F16V戰機下，F16戰機製造商、美國軍工企業洛歇馬丁（Lockheed Martin，簡稱洛馬）昨和台灣戰機製造及維修商漢翔簽署合作協議，推動台灣成為F16V戰機的亞太維修中心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與洛歇馬丁簽協議<br />\n<br />\n漢翔董事長胡開宏昨在台中漢翔沙鹿廠區與洛馬副總經理霍華德（Randy Howard）簽署合作協議。行政院長蘇貞昌致詞時表示，國防需要空防，空防需要戰機，戰機需要維修，希望雙方合作愉快、創造雙贏。胡開宏表示，漢翔身為台灣航太產業龍頭，將透過洛馬協助，積極爭取零件製造、技術轉移，最終希望盡快成立維修中心，成為台灣空軍F16機隊維修保養最堅強的後盾。<br />\n<br />\n台政府斥資1,100億元新台幣（284億港元）委託洛馬公司與漢翔，將台灣空軍現有的144架F16A/B升級為F16V，若再加上台灣同步向美國採購66架全新F16V戰機，台灣未來擁有的F16機隊數量多達210架，將成為亞太地區最大使用地區。<br />\n<br />\n台方一直爭取洛馬在台設立F16V戰機亞太維修中心，距離台灣大選不到四星期，終於傳來好消息，雙方簽約落實合作，一方面顯示台美加強軍事合作，另一方面展示蔡英文「國機國造」政策上的成果。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"002f55787d3b037eb06ee28725cde1209b9db7f4","tid":1788050,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T11:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0suoQ2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0suoQ2O.jpg&h=203fa15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"919fba9ec8e5077c016d9b8e0c32a0fa6c850464","tid":1788050,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T11:01:27.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c596c3702ee5803c80497f7f179eba96919a1b05","tid":1788050,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T11:07:26.000Z","msg":"對岸啲垃圾驚到瀨屎未"}]}